trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument" /> objects that are stored as key/value pairs.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de objetos <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument" /> que são armazenados como pares chave-valor.

trans-unit.source: Each element in an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract> is a key/value pair that is stored in a <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry> object.
trans-unit.target: Cada elemento em uma <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract> é um par chave/valor que é armazenado em um <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry> objeto.

trans-unit.source: Each key/value pair must have a unique key.
trans-unit.target: Cada par chave/valor deve ter uma chave exclusiva.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract> interface enables the contained keys and values to be enumerated, but it does not imply any particular sort order.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract> interface permite que as chaves independentes e valores a serem enumerados, mas isso não significa que uma ordem de classificação específica.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument" /> to use as the key of the element to add.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument" /> a ser usado como chave do elemento a ser adicionado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument" /> to use as the value of the element to add.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument" /> a ser usado como valor do elemento a ser adicionado.

trans-unit.source: Adds an element with a specified key and value to the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona um elemento com uma chave e um valor especificados no <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.

trans-unit.source: An element with the same key already exists in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
trans-unit.target: Já existe um elemento com a mesma chave no <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.

trans-unit.source: Removes all elements from the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
trans-unit.target: Remove todos os elementos do <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.

trans-unit.source: The key to locate in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
trans-unit.target: A chave a ser localizada no <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> contains an element with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: Indica se o <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> contém um elemento com a chave especificada.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> contains an element with the specified key; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> contiver um elemento com a chave especificada; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract" /> that can be used to iterate through the elements in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract" /> que pode ser usado para iterar nos elementos nos <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract" /> that can be used to iterate through the elements in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract" /> que pode ser usado para iterar nos elementos nos <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: Os enumeradores podem ser usados para ler os dados na coleção, mas não podem ser usados para modificar a coleção subjacente.

trans-unit.source: The key of the value to return.
trans-unit.target: A chave do valor a ser retornado.

trans-unit.source: Returns the value of the element with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: Retorna o valor do elemento com a chave especificada.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument" /> with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument" /> com a chave especificada.

trans-unit.source: Returns an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentCollectionContract" /> that contains the keys of the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentCollectionContract" /> que contém as chaves do objeto <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentCollectionContract" /> that contains the keys of the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentCollectionContract" /> que contém as chaves do objeto <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentCollectionContract" /> that contains the values of the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentCollectionContract" /> que contém os valores do objeto <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentCollectionContract" /> that contains the values of the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentCollectionContract" /> que contém os valores do objeto <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.

trans-unit.source: The key of the element to remove.
trans-unit.target: A chave do elemento a ser removido.

trans-unit.source: Removes the element with the specified key from the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
trans-unit.target: Remove o elemento com a chave especificada do <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the element is successfully found and removed; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o elemento for encontrado e removido com êxito; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: This method returns <see langword="false" /> if <paramref name="key" /> is not found in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.
trans-unit.target: Esse método retorna <see langword="false" /> se <paramref name="key" /> não foi encontrado no <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract" />.

trans-unit.source: The key of the value to replace.
trans-unit.target: A chave do valor a ser substituído.

trans-unit.source: The new value of the specified element.
trans-unit.target: O novo valor do elemento especificado.

trans-unit.source: Replaces the value of an element.
trans-unit.target: Substitui o valor de um elemento.
